          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 col-12 why-choose-item">
            <div class="why-choose-icon">
              <img
                src="../../assets/icons/patient-care.svg"
                alt="Patient centred approach"
                height="60"
                width="60"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="why-choose-text">Patient centred approach for quality care.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 col-12 why-choose-item">
            <div class="why-choose-icon">
              <img
                src="../../assets/icons/tick.svg"
                alt="Excellent customer service"
                height="60"
                width="60"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="why-choose-text">
              Excellent customer service and attention to patient care.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 col-12 why-choose-item">
            <div class="why-choose-icon">
              <img
