              Positive reviews and testimonials from satisfied clients.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Service intro -->
    <section class="what-is-drip-section">
      <h1>Tele-consultation service</h1>
      <p class="m-5 mt-0">
        Healthcarebia’s Doctor on Call service brings the expertise of DHA certified medical
        professionals directly to your doorstep. With the convenience of a doctor at home, you can
        receive medical consultations, examinations, and treatments without leaving your residence.
        This service ensures personalized care, prompt attention, and peace of mind for your
        healthcare needs.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Benefits -->
    <section class="what-is-drip-section">
      <div class="what-is-block mb-5 mt-3">
        <div class="row">
          <img
            src="../../assets/img/doctor-on-call-benefits.jpg"
            alt="Doctor on Call benefits illustration"
            class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12"
          />
          <div class="col-lg-8 p-5 col-md-6 col-12 benefits-block">
            <h4 class="py-4">Services provided on Call</h4>
            <ul class="pb-4">
              <li>
                <img src="../../assets/icons/down-arrow-white.svg" alt="" height="20" width="20" />
                <span
                  >Medical consultations and teleconsultations for various health concerns and
                  conditions.</span
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <img src="../../assets/icons/down-arrow-white.svg" alt="" height="20" width="20" />
                <span
                  >Diagnostic tests such as blood work, DNA analysis and Health check
                  packages.</span
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <img src="../../assets/icons/down-arrow-white.svg" alt="" height="20" width="20" />
                <span
                  >Chronic disease management, including monitoring and medication
                  adjustments.</span
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <img src="../../assets/icons/down-arrow-white.svg" alt="" height="20" width="20" />
                <span>Physical examinations from the comfort of your home.</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <img src="../../assets/icons/down-arrow-white.svg" alt="" height="20" width="20" />
                <span>Prescription and management of medications.</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <img src="../../assets/icons/down-arrow-white.svg" alt="" height="20" width="20" />
                <span>Diagnosis and treatment of illnesses and minor injuries.</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <img src="../../assets/icons/down-arrow-white.svg" alt="" height="20" width="20" />
                <span>Home-based medical procedures, such as wound care or injections.</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <img src="../../assets/icons/down-arrow-white.svg" alt="" height="20" width="20" />
                <span>Referrals to specialists or diagnostic tests, if necessary.</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <img src="../../assets/icons/down-arrow-white.svg" alt="" height="20" width="20" />
                <span
                  >Patient education and counselling on healthcare management and lifestyle
                  modifications.</span
                >
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services provided at home -->
    <section class="how-drip-works-section mt-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="how-drip-works-left col-md-7">
          <h1 class="my-5">Benefits of Doctor on Call Service</h1>

          <p class="mb-5">
            Convenient access to quality medical care from the comfort of your home, eliminating the
            need to travel and wait in crowded clinics or hospitals. Receive personalized, complete
            attention from a qualified healthcare professional tailored to your individual needs.
            ideal for people with mobility issues, busy schedules, or anyone seeking privacy in
            their healthcare.
          </p>

          <a href="https://wa.me/971547077476"
            ><button class="mb-5">Book your home visit</button></a
          >
        </div>
        <div class="how-drip-works-right col-md-5 d-flex justify-content-end align-items-end">
          <img
            src="../../assets/img/doctor-on-call-services.jpg"
            alt="Doctor visiting home"
            height="500"
            width="500"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faqs pb-5">
      <h1 class="my-5 pt-3 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <div class="row mx-5">
        <!-- Column A -->
        <div class="accordion col-md-6 col-12 p-3" id="accordion">
          <!-- 1 -->
          <div class="accordion-item mb-3 rounded-4">
            <h2 class="accordion-header rounded-4" id="heading01">
              <button
                class="accordion-button d-flex gap-1"
                type="button"
                data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#collapse01"
                aria-expanded="true"
                aria-controls="collapse01"
              >
                <div class="question-icon">
                  <img src="../assets/icons/Question mrk.svg" alt="Question mark icon" />
                </div>
                <span>1. How can I schedule a doctor at home visit?</span>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id="collapse01"
              class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
              aria-labelledby="heading01"
              data-bs-parent="#accordion"
            >
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Book via phone, WhatsApp, or our online form. Choose your preferred time and
                location; our coordinator confirms details and dispatches a DHA-licensed clinician.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 2 -->
          <div class="accordion-item mb-3 rounded-4">
            <h2 class="accordion-header rounded-4" id="heading02">
              <button
                class="accordion-button collapsed d-flex gap-1"
                type="button"
                data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#collapse02"
                aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapse02"
              >
                <div class="question-icon">
                  <img src="../assets/icons/Question mrk.svg" alt="Question mark icon" />
                </div>
                <span>2. What conditions can be treated by a doctor at home?</span>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id="collapse02"
              class="accordion-collapse collapse"
              aria-labelledby="heading02"
              data-bs-parent="#accordion"
            >
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Common illnesses (fever, flu, stomach upset), infections, migraines, skin rashes,
                allergies, musculoskeletal pain, minor injuries, prescription refills, wound care,
                injections, and IV therapies. We’ll triage and advise if a hospital visit is more
                appropriate.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 3 -->
          <div class="accordion-item mb-3 rounded-4">
            <h2 class="accordion-header rounded-4" id="heading03">
              <button
                class="accordion-button collapsed d-flex gap-1"
                type="button"
                data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#collapse03"
                aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapse03"
              >
                <div class="question-icon">
                  <img src="../assets/icons/Question mrk.svg" alt="Question mark icon" />
                </div>
                <span>3. Is a doctor at home visit covered by insurance?</span>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id="collapse03"
              class="accordion-collapse collapse"
              aria-labelledby="heading03"
              data-bs-parent="#accordion"
            >
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Coverage varies by plan. Many home visits are self-pay; if your policy covers home
                care, we can provide invoices/medical reports for reimbursement. Please check your
                insurer for eligibility and pre-approval requirements.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Column B -->
        <div class="accordion col-md-6 col-12 p-3" id="accordionB">
          <!-- 4 -->
          <div class="accordion-item mb-3 rounded-4">
            <h2 class="accordion-header rounded-4" id="heading04B">
              <button
                class="accordion-button d-flex gap-1"
                type="button"
                data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#collapse04B"
                aria-expanded="true"
                aria-controls="collapse04B"
              >
                <div class="question-icon">
                  <img src="../assets/icons/Question mrk.svg" alt="Question mark icon" />
                </div>
                <span>4. How long does a typical doctor at home visit last?</span>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id="collapse04B"
              class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
              aria-labelledby="heading04B"
              data-bs-parent="#accordionB"
            >
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Most visits take 30–45 minutes, depending on assessment complexity, diagnostics, and
                treatments provided.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 5 -->
          <div class="accordion-item mb-3 rounded-4">
            <h2 class="accordion-header rounded-4" id="heading05B">
              <button
                class="accordion-button collapsed d-flex gap-1"
                type="button"
                data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#collapse05B"
                aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapse05B"
              >
                <div class="question-icon">
                  <img src="../assets/icons/Question mrk.svg" alt="Question mark icon" />
                </div>
                <span>5. Can a doctor at home provide emergency medical care?</span>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id="collapse05B"
              class="accordion-collapse collapse"
              aria-labelledby="heading05B"
              data-bs-parent="#accordionB"
            >
              <div class="accordion-body">
                For life-threatening symptoms (severe chest pain, heavy bleeding, loss of
                consciousness), call 998 immediately. Our clinicians can stabilize
                non-life-threatening issues and arrange transfer if needed.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 6 -->
          <div class="accordion-item mb-3 rounded-4">
            <h2 class="accordion-header rounded-4" id="heading06B">
              <button
                class="accordion-button collapsed d-flex gap-1"
                type="button"
                data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#collapse06B"
                aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapse06B"
              >
                <div class="question-icon">
                  <img src="../assets/icons/Question mrk.svg" alt="Question mark icon" />
                </div>
                <span>6. Are doctor at home visits available during weekends and holidays?</span>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id="collapse06B"
              class="accordion-collapse collapse"
              aria-labelledby="heading06B"
              data-bs-parent="#accordionB"
            >
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Yes. We’re available 7 days a week, 365 days a year. Same-day bookings are often
                possible based on slot availability.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <%- include("../partials/footer.ejs") %> <%- include("../partials/footer-tags.ejs") %>
  </body>
</html>
